cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a method for crowd counting using multiple CNNs specialized to specific appearances, which is a common approach in computer vision (cs.CV). The method also involves adaptively selecting the CNNs based on the appearance of the test image, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves experiments and evaluations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
